title: Gated Access, Lounging and Sunbathing Areas, Vertical Blinds
posting_body: ['Located in the heart of Canyon Country near Santa Clarita, Diamond Park Apartments brings you incredible amenities and comfort in a beautiful and convenient Southern California location.', 'With several airy floor plans to choose from, top-of-the-line kitchen designs, private balconies and patios, and easy access to the best of Santa Clarita and Canyon Country, our one and two bedroom apartments for rent offer exquisite living at an affordable price.', 'At Diamond Park in Canyon Country, just minutes from the heart of Santa Clarita, CA we have apartments to meet all your needs for both space and style.', 'APARTMENT FEATURES', '-Central Air Conditioning', '-Vertical Blinds', '-Whirlpool Appliances', '-Double Stainless Steel Sinks', '-Walk-in Closets', '-Washer/Dryer in Each Apartment Home', '-Pre-Wired For Telephone and Cable', '-Custom Oak Cabinets', '-Large Private Balcony/Patio', 'COMMUNITY AMENITIES', '-Two', 'Playgrounds', '-Barbecue and Picnic Areas with Tables', '-On-site Maintenance', '-Soothing Whirlpool Spa/Hot Tub', '-Easy Access to Freeways & Shopping', '-Beautiful Landscaping', '-Lounging and Sunbathing Areas', '-Gated Access', '-Carport Available', '-Shimmering Swimming Pool', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'WEBSITE', '<URL>', 'ADDRESS', '27940 Solamint Rd., Canyon Country, CA 91387', 'Pricing and availability are subject to change.']
